Question.Subject: How do I restore previous websites in the address bar--FIREFOX?
Question.Content: I don't know what happened but I can't see the previous websites I've typed into the address bar anymore. It's kind of annoying to type in the whole address again without having it pop up automatically. How do i fix this? Thanks.
Question.ChosenAnswer: Check your history and see if it was deleted. You might have to update it as well because there was a recent update. If your history was deleted then you will have to then type everything back in.

Answer.Content: Check your history and see if it was deleted. You might have to update it as well because there was a recent update. If your history was deleted then you will have to then type everything back in.
